847    /**

853        ProductImportBuilder builder = new ProductImportBuilder();
854        builder.key = template.getKey();
855        builder.name = template.getName();
856        builder.productType = template.getProductType();
857        builder.slug = template.getSlug();
858        builder.description = template.getDescription();
859        builder.categories = template.getCategories();
860        builder.metaTitle = template.getMetaTitle();
861        builder.metaDescription = template.getMetaDescription();
862        builder.metaKeywords = template.getMetaKeywords();
863        builder.taxCategory = template.getTaxCategory();
864        builder.searchKeywords = template.getSearchKeywords();
865        builder.state = template.getState();
866        builder.publish = template.getPublish();
867        builder.priceMode = template.getPriceMode();
868        return builder;
